[p 
	"Shapeshifting dogs. Evil robots. Alchemy. Cheesy B movie references. These are all par for the course in 
	[em 
		"Secret of Evermore
	]em
	", a very loose "sequel" to 
	[em 
		[a class=intlink href=/Game/Snes-secret-of-mana 
			"Secret of Mana
		]a
	]em
	". The story follows a boy that is thrust into a virtual world and finds himself with no immediate means to escape. As the boy travels, the geography changes to reflect certain eras of real-life history, adding a unique aspect to the game.
]p
